Ques: What is executition plan in DB ?
Ans: An execution plan is the strategy generated by the database query optimizer that defines how a SQL query will be executed. It includes details like whether an index scan or full table scan will be used, 
join methods, and estimated cost. It helps improve query performance by showing how data is accessed internally.

